4 Pomo is the only valley pizzeria to be certified by the Verace Pizza Napoletana Association. I don't really know what this means, but my taste buds don't care. The organic precision of this pizza topples most so-called italian eateries here in the valley. The atmosphere is simple, casual and perfect for any time of the day. The dough is clearly made from scratch as the fire blisters the crust and the fresh ingredients melt in your mouth. My favorite is "BIANCA Mozzarella Fior di Latte, Prosciutto Crudo San" followed up with homemade Cannoli's.
